ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It is a required course. The content is appropriate for a required course. It is not particularly inspiring and there is little room for personal interest. I did not take the class by choice and I probably wouldn't have taken it if I had had the option.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course didn't really deepen my knowledge. I took similar courses when I was an undergraduate. I expect it was more helpful for the undergraduates in the course. The course contributed to my research because it gave me a chance to design a research grant proposal.
